{"tid":445564,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖] 金錢外貌都沒差　烏克蘭妹超想嫁出國：人好我就嫁","createTime":"2017-10-23T13:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T03:59:16.000Z","uid":64544,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"69bae1728112f1f1c303c3a83e36de17c751d3c3","tid":445564,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭婚介公司看好中國市場發展潛力大，徵婚者質素又高，所以除了網上聊天，婚介公司亦會舉辦相親團，安排中國男士遠赴烏克蘭與烏克蘭女生見面。婚介網站「<a href=\"http://SlavicLady.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FSlavicLady.com&d=78JB%2BGYRbRxacVZBcvZYcTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ecb98492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">SlavicLady.com</a>」負責人Irish說。「中國人對烏克蘭的認識非常片面，甚至仍以為我們屬於蘇聯。」因此，Irish的公司便組織旅行團讓有興趣的男士報名起行，加深對烏克蘭的了解。<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》記者實地來到烏克蘭街頭，訪問當地少女對跨國戀愛的看法，結果發現，她們普遍對外國男人都抱持開放態度，並強調國籍不會是發展關係的障礙，「金錢、長相都不重要，只要他人好我就嫁。」即使從未交過華人朋友，也覺得沒差。<br />\n<br />\n對於女生超想嫁出國的現象，烏克蘭當地男性又是怎麼想？有人認為，「如果那外國男人條件真是很好，那有甚麼問題？但如果是20歲的女人嫁給一個老頭，那就只有一個原因－錢。」另一個烏克蘭男性也言之鑿鑿：「大部份的海外婚姻都是基於錢，可能她們想快速致富，但我不認同這種婚姻會帶來幸福結局。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/211757_9125d2b8d21daf58ba95c4a1b3cc1cca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F211757_9125d2b8d21daf58ba95c4a1b3cc1cca.jpg&h=7b86f6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婚介公司會舉辦相親團，安排中國男士遠赴烏克蘭與當地女生見面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/211906_d3fff44daf66606ac3b9e02a44dc96ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F211906_d3fff44daf66606ac3b9e02a44dc96ce.jpg&h=63f3d214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏克蘭女性普遍對外國男人都抱持開放態度，並強調國籍不會是發展關係的障礙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/211940_81d949c9a7213f1761e347f5d151fa85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F211940_81d949c9a7213f1761e347f5d151fa85.jpg&h=f4c080b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏克蘭女性普遍身材高䠷，五官標致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20171022/1226732/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20171022%2F1226732%2F&d=78JB%2BGYRbRxacVZBcvZYcTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2f42613c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20171022/1226732/</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔幾時組團去烏克蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4cf888e0d6dbd7834209e5368b491eddb7c796","tid":445564,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"真係沒差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e84334004bec77517916f6e82451781fc1221b6","tid":445564,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ed95f1252c9da5d5bb046f37342f7e1fac4123","tid":445564,"uid":60686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口裏說不貪錢"},{"pid":"48588b2222b60739338fa96cfbab818f8ce62b4f","tid":445564,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"個大陸仔老是常出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1574a8b0a938fb59d5ba0d57485f8e9de4e126d","tid":445564,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"有錢再諗"},{"pid":"198bd05c1baa4c5dafcc2006a2b88902e3f0547d","tid":445564,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73997.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F73997.jpg&h=37891031&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceabfb1b8e25e9a630ddfea53dfb66b68b189d6e","tid":445564,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/225840_943f2b0aa171125a8fa14703ebe05ac9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F225840_943f2b0aa171125a8fa14703ebe05ac9.jpg&h=ff930735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來外貌都沒差就係咁嘅樣"},{"pid":"f5b6e8a688eba29bb013989d20c1db740ca71117","tid":445564,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"冇錢得鬼閒嫁又樣衰又瘦亞洲佬咩<br />\n揀番自己人唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68f968462e8a36a427897c4e31b105692a181f1","tid":445564,"uid":45749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇錢得鬼閒嫁又樣衰又瘦亞洲佬咩<br />\n揀番自己人唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港大學生中位收入已經係烏克蘭中產水平<br />\n佢地人均收入都係五千幾左右<br />\n佢地嫁到黎香港已經係脫貧"},{"pid":"d2d62dfab045bf7b256d796aba88b7f084ce31b8","tid":445564,"uid":78620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭早2年俾俄羅斯攪, 家陣經濟應該仲係好差"},{"pid":"779f222c5e785b62a1385dbd44eeacae33f9952f","tid":445564,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"日日食洋腸<br />\n未試過臘腸又點知好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634b5af6a9d4768ff48a2e08a83d98c5169a08de","tid":445564,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:40:43.000Z","msg":"生出來既顏值高,呢個係窮撚俾到父蔭既機會"},{"pid":"7a1609f8907f8a36cb83213d72168ea3ba28bb17","tid":445564,"uid":61015,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTim